+"""Incremental, targeted-repair, restart, and fresh-rebuild equivalence.
+
+The oracle in this module is the planted demo source plus declared transform
+invariants.  It deliberately does not serialize the incremental database and
+call that the expected rebuild result.  The two active generations are
+projected independently through exact derivation keys and each projection is
+also checked against hard-coded fixture facts.
+"""
+
